NAME
    Error::Pure::ANSIColor - Error::Pure modules with Term::ANSIColor
    support.

DESCRIPTION
    List of modules:

    "Error::Pure::ANSIColor::AllError"
            Print full backtrace with Term::ANSIColor support.

    "Error::Pure::ANSIColor::Die"
            Die with Term::ANSIColor support.

    "Error::Pure::ANSIColor::Error"
            Print error on one line with Term::ANSIColor support.

    "Error::Pure::ANSIColor::ErrorList"
            Print list of errors with ANSIColor support. Each error on one
            line.

    "Error::Pure::ANSIColor::Print"
            Print error as simple string with ANSIColor support

SEE ALSO
    Task::Error::Pure
        Install the Error::Pure modules.

REPOSITORY
    <https://github.com/tupinek/Error-Pure-ANSIColor>

